snippet.title: Cat or Ice Cream? Game Trailer
snippet.description:
'Cat or Ice Cream?' is the first game ever created by Shannon Jahnel Lanktree and Sam Bunny. It was made in 7 days as part of the notGDCJam2020 and uses two of the theme requirements Feline and Ice Cream.

Play Cat or Ice Cream?:
https://cookiecrayon.itch.io/cat-or-ice-cream

Shannon Jahnel Lanktree
https://syrupsprinkles.com/
